HE KEEPS SAYING

16:24.358 --> 16:26.110
HE'S GONNA EXPLODE.

16:26.152 --> 16:27.862
KIND OF IN THE MIDDLE

16:26.152 --> 16:27.862
OF SOMETHING HERE.

16:27.904 --> 16:29.029
OH. OKAY.

16:29.071 --> 16:31.198
NO, I'LL DO IT.

16:29.071 --> 16:31.198
THAT'S FINE.

16:31.240 --> 16:33.033
BUT I AM GOING TO CABO

16:31.240 --> 16:33.033
AT THE END OF THE MONTH

16:33.075 --> 16:35.912
WITH MY SISTER,

16:33.075 --> 16:35.912
AND I'M DRINKING TEQUILA.

16:38.080 --> 16:40.708
THERE'S A LITTLE BOY IN THERE,

16:38.080 --> 16:40.708
AND THAT WEIRDS ME OUT.

16:40.750 --> 16:45.045
AARON, I-I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU

16:40.750 --> 16:45.045
AND THERESA ENDED UP TOGETHER.

16:45.087 --> 16:46.130
(Theresa) LIVIN' THE DREAM!

16:46.172 --> 16:47.465
GUESS IT WAS FATE.

16:47.507 --> 16:50.343
YEAH. OR IT WAS ME.

16:47.507 --> 16:50.343
(chuckles)

16:50.384 --> 16:52.470
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

16:52.512 --> 16:57.057
WELL, IF, YOU KNOW,

16:52.512 --> 16:57.057
I'D GOTTEN THERESA EXPELLED,

16:57.099 --> 16:59.059
THINGS MIGHT'VE TURNED OUT

16:57.099 --> 16:59.059
DIFFERENTLY.

16:59.101 --> 17:02.062
YOU KNOW, MAYBE YOU AND I

16:59.101 --> 17:02.062
WOULD'VE KEPT ON DATING.

17:02.104 --> 17:04.064
MAYBE WE'D STILL BE DATING.

17:04.106 --> 17:07.067
WHO KNOWS? MAYBE I'D BE

17:04.106 --> 17:07.067
THE ONE IN THERE IN THE STALL,

17:07.109 --> 17:08.319
HELPING A.J. GO.

17:08.361 --> 17:10.488
(Theresa) HEY, GET IN HERE,

17:08.361 --> 17:10.488
HONEY! KNOCK YOURSELF OUT!

17:10.530 --> 17:13.992
JUNE, THIS PICTURE

17:10.530 --> 17:13.992
THAT YOU'RE PAINTING...

17:14.033 --> 17:15.535
DO YOU REALLY WANT IT?

17:15.576 --> 17:17.161
DO YOU REALLY WANNA

17:15.576 --> 17:17.161
LIVE HERE

17:17.203 --> 17:20.164
WITH THIS GUY AND THAT BABY

17:17.203 --> 17:20.164
AND THESE LOBSTERS?

17:20.206 --> 17:22.249
WELL, I...

17:22.291 --> 17:23.751
OR DID YOU JUST GET HUNG UP

17:22.291 --> 17:23.751
ON THE IDEA

17:23.793 --> 17:26.587
BECAUSE YOU THOUGHT THIS GUY

17:23.793 --> 17:26.587
WAS THE ONE WHO GOT AWAY?

17:28.214 --> 17:30.090
YOU'RE RIGHT.

17:30.132 --> 17:33.386
WHAT AM I TALKING ABOUT?

17:30.132 --> 17:33.386
I-I DON'T WANT THIS.

17:33.427 --> 17:35.179
I WANT THIS.

17:35.221 --> 17:37.097
OH, I KNEW IT.

17:37.139 --> 17:39.017
JUNE, I KISSED THOSE GIRLS

17:39.058 --> 17:40.768
TO ILLUSTRATE HOW BORING

17:39.058 --> 17:40.768
YOUR STORY WAS.

17:40.810 --> 17:44.104
IF I MISLED YOU IN SOME WAY,

17:40.810 --> 17:44.104
I'M--

17:40.810 --> 17:44.104
NO! NO!

17:44.146 --> 17:46.106
I WANT WHAT YOU REPRESENT--

17:46.148 --> 17:49.360
MY LIFE IN NEW YORK,

17:46.148 --> 17:49.360
THE LIFE THAT I ALREADY HAVE.

17:49.402 --> 17:52.154
SEE? I TOLD YOU. YOU MAKE

17:49.402 --> 17:52.154
A BIG MOVE AND YOU GET CLARITY.

17:52.196 --> 17:53.531
YOU JUST HAD TO GET AARON DeMAYO

17:52.196 --> 17:53.531
OUT OF YOUR SYSTEM,

17:53.573 --> 17:55.115
THE SAME WAY I HAD TO DO

17:53.573 --> 17:55.115
WITH BENJAMIN.

17:55.157 --> 17:57.410
OH, BENJAMIN IS THIS GUY

17:55.157 --> 17:57.410
THAT I GOT DEPORTED.

17:57.451 --> 17:58.578
IT'S A REALLY LONG STORY,

17:58.619 --> 18:00.120
BUT I'LL TELL YOU ABOUT IT

17:58.619 --> 18:00.120
RIGHT NOW.

18:00.162 --> 18:02.122
(Chloe) WE WERE FINALLY GOING

18:00.162 --> 18:02.122
TO BE IN THE SAME CITY

18:02.164 --> 18:03.750
FOR A LONG STRETCH OF TIME,

18:03.791 --> 18:05.543
SO WE DECIDED TO HAVE SEX IN

18:03.791 --> 18:05.543
BATHROOMS EVERYWHERE WE COULD.

18:05.585 --> 18:07.587
WE DID IT IN MY APARTMENT,

18:05.585 --> 18:07.587
DIANE SAWYER'S DRESSING ROOM,

18:07.628 --> 18:08.755
AN R.V...

18:08.796 --> 18:10.130
OH, MY GOD.

18:08.796 --> 18:10.130
WHAT AM I DOING?

18:10.172 --> 18:11.340
WHY AM I TALKING ABOUT

18:11.382 --> 18:12.383
SOMETHING THAT HAPPENED

18:11.382 --> 18:12.383
A MILLION YEARS AGO?

18:12.425 --> 18:13.634
THAT WAS YESTERDAY.

18:13.676 --> 18:15.386
EXACTLY!

18:13.676 --> 18:15.386
WHY HAVEN'T I MOVED ON?

18:15.428 --> 18:17.096
CAN SOMEONE HAND ME

18:15.428 --> 18:17.096
ALL THE PAPER TOWELS?

18:19.181 --> 18:21.935
YOU HAVEN'T MOVED ON YET

18:19.181 --> 18:21.935
BECAUSE HE'S STILL

18:21.976 --> 18:23.978
IN THERE AND THERE,

18:24.020 --> 18:25.855
EVEN THOUGH

18:24.020 --> 18:25.855
HE'S NOT IN THERE.

18:25.897 --> 18:28.566
I'M NOT OVER HIM.

18:30.192 --> 18:32.319
(knock on door)

18:32.361 --> 18:33.613
OCCUPIED.

18:33.654 --> 18:35.239
(Derek) IT'S YOUR CAPTAIN.

18:39.702 --> 18:40.954
HEY, I'M--I'M DEREK.

18:40.995 --> 18:43.247
UH, NUMBER THREE

18:40.995 --> 18:43.247
IN CHLOE'S ROTATION.

18:43.289 --> 18:45.165
YOU HAVE A PHONE CALL.

18:49.879 --> 18:52.172
HELLO?

18:49.879 --> 18:52.172
SORRY. I'M SORRY.

18:52.214 --> 18:54.675
WHAT THE HELL, CHLOE?!

18:52.214 --> 18:54.675
