18:54.717 --> 18:56.176
I CAN'T COME BACK TO THE STATES

18:54.717 --> 18:56.176
FOR A YEAR!

18:56.218 --> 18:58.304
FINE! SCREW YOU!

18:56.218 --> 18:58.304
(beep)

