THIS IS ME TRYING TO APOLOGIZE.

19:03.893 --> 19:06.186
ALL RIGHT?

19:06.228 --> 19:07.396
I'M SORRY.

19:07.438 --> 19:08.815
WHY'D YOU DO IT?

19:08.856 --> 19:11.191
I... HAD TO.

19:11.233 --> 19:14.070
YOU SAID MELINDA WAS YOUR

19:11.233 --> 19:14.070
NUMBER ONE, AND I GOT JEALOUS.

19:14.112 --> 19:15.613
WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY ANYTHING?

19:15.655 --> 19:19.283
YOU COULD'VE TALKED TO ME ABOUT

19:15.655 --> 19:19.283
IT INSTEAD OF RUINING MY LIFE.

19:19.325 --> 19:21.452
BECAUSE I DON'T WANT

19:19.325 --> 19:21.452
TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT THIS.

19:21.494 --> 19:24.122
I DON'T WANT TO WANT THIS.

19:24.163 --> 19:26.916
I MEAN, MAYBE SOMEDAY DOWN

19:24.163 --> 19:26.916
THE ROAD, WHEN WE'RE OLD...

19:26.958 --> 19:28.208
