I'M SORRY THAT I DID THIS

19:33.756 --> 19:35.257
TO YOU.

19:35.299 --> 19:36.509
THANK YOU.

19:36.550 --> 19:38.218
BUT I'M NOT SORRY

19:36.550 --> 19:38.218
I DID THIS FOR ME.

19:38.260 --> 19:40.220
I'M NOT READY FOR ALL THIS.

19:40.262 --> 19:42.222
I GET IT.

19:42.264 --> 19:45.018
MAYBE SOMEDAY.

19:45.059 --> 19:46.435
YOU'RE GONNA HANG UP ON ME NOW,

19:45.059 --> 19:46.435
